 "system": "openfrp74",
 "category": "hirelings",
 "description": "Hired fighters — men, dwarves, elves, or (for the Chaotic) Orcs at half a man's upkeep. Monthly cost in GP: Non-Fighter 1; Light Foot 2 (Orc 1); Heavy Foot 3/4/5/1.5 (man/dwarf/elf/orc); Archer 5 (elf 10, orc 3); Crossbowman 4 (dwarf 5); Longbowman 10; Light/Medium/Heavy Horseman 10/15/20. To hire either class: post notices or send servitors at 100-600 GP a week; generosity governs success, and Elves, Dwarves, and specialists are scarce.",
